name: Metathings
description: What is the project about? Metathings ($METT) aims to transform 2D objects into 3D NFTs using artificial intelligence. It transforms a 2D photo given to it into 3D in a very short time and mints it as NFT What makes your project unique? Metathings will be the first app to adapt AI Object Modeling to Blockchains (AOMB) History of your project. Our project started life as an idea about a year ago, and a section containing our story was added in the whitepaper. Whatâ€™s next for your project? The next step of the project is the release of the demo version of the 3D NFT mint platform, which is currently being tested by the project followers. Also staking dapp is ready and staking will start. What can your token be used for? METT will be used to produce 3D NFTs. And after each nft mint, the paid mett token will be burned. In addition, Mett tokens will be used for staking.
